      <li class="c5"><span class="c2">Risk of MTX Mining Attacks: </span><span class="c0">As with other decentralized cryptographic tokens and cryptocurrencies, the blockchain used for the Matryx platform is susceptible to mining attacks, including double-spend attacks, majority mining power attacks, selfish-mining attacks, and race condition attacks. Any successful attacks present a risk to the Matryx platform, MTX, and expected proper execution and sequencing of Ethereum contract computations. &nbsp;Despite the efforts of the Matryx team, the risk of known or novel mining attacks exists.</span></li>
